---
layout: base.njk
title: Leaderboards
---
<h1 style="margin-bottom: 5px;">Leaderboards</h1>
<p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 30px;">
  Disciplines and journals with the most approved nominations.
</p>

<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px;">
  
  <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h3 class="serif" style="margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 10px;">Most Nominated Disciplines</h3>
    <ul style="line-height: 1.8; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
      {% for item in leaderboards.disciplines %}
        <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding: 5px 0;">
          <strong>{{ item.name }}</strong> 
          <span style="color: var(--link); font-weight: 600;">{{ item.count }}</span>
        </li>
      {% else %}
        <li style="color: #666;">No discipline data available yet.</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h3 class="serif" style="margin-top: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 10px;">Most Nominated Journals</h3>
    <ul style="line-height: 1.8; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0;">
      {% for item in leaderboards.journals %}
        <li style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding: 5px 0;">
          <strong>{{ item.name }}</strong> 
          <span style="color: var(--link); font-weight: 600;">{{ item.count }}</span>
        </li>
      {% else %}
        <li style="color: #666;">No journal data available yet.</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

</div>
